dct_title_s: Carte de la région du Lac St.-Jean, province du Québec : préparée au Département de la Colonisation et des Travaux-Publics, d'après les plans du service au arpentages
dct_description_sm: Map of the Lake Saint John region, Québec province. Prepared by the Department of Colonization and Public Works, according to plans by the survey service. Drawn by Rosario Genest.; Shows municipalities and lot divisions.; "Québec, Aout, 1901."; "Échelle: 2 milles au pouce."; University Libraries' copy is sectioned horizontally into two pieces.
dct_publisher_sm: Département de la Colonisation et des Travaux-Publics (Québec)
